Package: rwevidence
Type: Package
Title: Real-World Evidence Generation for Pharmaceutical Research
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Gagandeep", "Singh", email = "gagans01399@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Author: Gagandeep Singh [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Gagandeep Singh <gagans01399@gmail.com>
Description: Provides end-to-end workflows for generating Real-World Evidence
    (RWE) from Real-World Data (RWD) sources. Includes data ingestion,
    quality assessment, harmonization, AI-powered analytics, external control
    arm generation, and regulatory-compliant reporting following FDA and EMA
    guidance.
